vote.title: An ordinance abandoning a portion of two sanitary sewer easements with temporary working space easements to Morrell LandCo LLC, the abutting owner, containing a total of approximately 1,419 square feet of land, located near the intersection of Morrell Avenue and Corinth Street - Revenue: General Fund $7,800.00, plus the $20.00 ordinance publication fee
